---
title: "FASTag — Current State Flow"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant V as Vehicle
    participant R as RFID Reader<br/>(at barrier)
    participant LC as Lane Controller
    participant TMS as Toll Management<br/>System
    participant PG as Payment Gateway<br/>(NPCI)
    participant B as Issuing Bank
    participant OP as Operator

    Note over V,OP: Vehicle arrives at toll gate and stops

    V->>LC: Vehicle detected (loop sensor)
    LC->>R: Activate reader
    R->>R: Attempt tag read (vehicle at 30–50cm)

    alt Tag read success
        R->>TMS: POST /process {tag_id} — synchronous HTTP
        TMS->>TMS: Database lookup (tag validation)
        TMS->>PG: POST /debit {tag_id, amount} — synchronous HTTP
        PG->>B: Debit request
        B-->>PG: Debit confirmation (variable latency)
        PG-->>TMS: Payment success
        TMS->>TMS: Write audit log — synchronous, in critical path
        TMS-->>LC: Open barrier signal
        LC->>V: Barrier raised
        Note over V,LC: Total time: 30 seconds — 5 minutes
    else Tag read failure (5–8% of transactions)
        R->>R: Retry (3 attempts, 5 seconds each)
        R-->>LC: Read failed
        LC->>OP: Alert: manual intervention required
        OP->>OP: Manually verify vehicle
        OP->>TMS: Manual override
        TMS->>PG: Process payment
        PG-->>TMS: Response
        TMS-->>LC: Open barrier
        LC->>V: Barrier raised
        Note over V,OP: Manual intervention: 3–8 minutes
        Note over OP: All queued vehicles wait during this time
    else Payment gateway timeout (3–5% of transactions)
        PG-->>TMS: Timeout (default: 30–120s)
        TMS-->>LC: Processing failed
        LC->>OP: Alert: payment timeout
        OP->>V: Direct vehicle to cash lane
        Note over V,OP: Timeout adds 2–5 minutes per incident
    end
